data.description: Come home to this spacious and beautiful one story house in a quiet neighborhood.  It features a real hardwood flooring, plantation shutters, huge pool sized backyard, 3 car garage and a covered patio. The home also includes, vaulted ceilings, extra Den, and upgraded stainless steel appliances.  Solar installed with energy bill as low as $15/mo
